title: PSVFRPC++Complete AAA PC VR Game Library With Playstation VR Hea
description: PSVFRPC++ Pack containes fully cracked copies of the current triple a vr game library for PC with added support for the Playstation VR headset. PSVFRPC++ includes a fully scripted setup package which installs and configures everything for you. All you need to do is install and play. PSVR headset driver provided by TrinusPSVR with time lock removed Check out the PSVFRPC++ website: http://psvfrpcplus.repo.plus Games included Doom VFR Skyrim VR Fallout 4 VR
